---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about me, my interests, and what I'm working on.">
  <main class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h1 class="about-title">About</h1>
      
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Who I Am</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I'm a builder, learner, and explorer. I like understanding why improbable things happen 
          and building things that matter. My work has largely lived at the intersection of 
          technology and real-world impact.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          I enjoy going down rabbit holes in opportunities I know little about, especially when 
          they challenge how I think. The experiences that force a shift in perspective, whether 
          comfortable or not, tend to stick with me the longest and matter the most.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">What I'm Learning</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I like learning through both study and experience. Currently exploring:
        </p>
        <ul class="interest-list">
          <li>Web development and modern frameworks</li>
          <li>Design principles and user experience</li>
          <li>Philosophy and systems thinking</li>
          <li>Building products that solve real problems</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Interests & Hobbies</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          When I'm not building, you might find me:
        </p>
        <ul class="interest-list">
          <li>Reading books on technology, design, and philosophy</li>
          <li>Exploring new technologies and frameworks</li>
          <li>Writing about things I've learned</li>
          <li>Contributing to open source projects</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="about-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Connect</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I'm always open to interesting conversations and collaborations. You can find me on:
        </p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="social-link">
            Email
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .interest-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .interest-list li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .interest-list li::before {
    content: 'Â·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #999;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-link {
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: #ccc;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    text-decoration-color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .interest-list li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>
